&lt;div id="outline-container-sec-7" class="outline-2"&gt; &lt;h2 id="sec-7"&gt;&lt;span class="section-number-2"&gt;7&lt;/span&gt; Finally getting my documents&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;div class="outline-text-2" id="text-7"&gt; &lt;p&gt; Here we get the EIDs from a search query. We use these in the next section to get a new bibliography. &lt;/p&gt;
